- OS Version: Windows_NT ia32 10.0.10586

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Attempt to use the `!global` flag to control SASS variable scope.

```
#main {
  $width: 5em !global;
  width: $width;
}

#sidebar {
  width: $width;
}

#footer {
 $footer-height: 40px !default !global;
  height: $footer-height;
}
```
1. Get the error `[scss] unknown keyword <global>`

- VSCode Version: 1.5.3
- OS Version: Win 10

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Create new file
2. switch to javascript language syntax
3. Paste that:

``` javascript
